{"tid":1130262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿球證判12碼予曼聯　尼馬網上鬧裁判被罰停賽3場","createTime":"2019-04-29T02:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T07:51:03.000Z","uid":186071,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"38e110e297be8422ef581b79fd0bfddd05431a43","tid":1130262,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:18:28.000Z","msg":"歐聯16強次回合，曼聯靠拉舒福特在完場前射入12碼，取得重要的作客入球，以3：1擊敗巴黎聖日耳門（PSG），兩回合踢成3：3，曼聯靠較多作客入球晉級。該仗因傷缺陣的PSG球星尼馬，賽後在社交網站怒轟裁判的決定，認為球證不應判罰12碼。"},{"pid":"3d0cc466da9a68021549aad1fbd8eba36fd86440","tid":1130262,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d7e36e3440c17a3fa65a0c8f1ea0737256aaba","tid":1130262,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"篇報道邊度有港停賽三場"},{"pid":"66b42c9f38da6505bcbc5f1e4156049783f75116","tid":1130262,"uid":40588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24d7e36e3440c17a3fa65a0c8f1ea0737256aaba","tid":1130262,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"篇報道邊度有港停賽三場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:36:06.000Z","msg":"尼馬自行停賽"},{"pid":"22f49148f586df05a3adc7e81a7d64390abd433d","tid":1130262,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"加埋係盃賽打球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隨時下季聯賽又停賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁聯賽同歐聯都停賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915676f96b076bc002bda38df5cc93a2d2c6adaf","tid":1130262,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"尼馬都係連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834b3766320e7f8221bc485eb99f8bc21a51fbe3","tid":1130262,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike"